  "description": [
    "navalog THE NAVYS OLDEST NEWSPAPER Vol 57No 38 Main Npy Exchange Changes Departments When the Main Retail Store Building 36 opens for business next Tuesday 24 Sept the var ious departments will have been completely reversed and re arranged There will also be two entrances to the store on the front side bordering Cushing Rd The changes are being effected due to the success of the present selfservice section Further ex pansion is impossible due to lack of space and the present arran gement is inconvenient due to the distance of this highvolume fastmoving merchandise from the stockroom The area which is now self service will be occupied by the Jewelry Camera Smoking Ac cessory Mens Accessory and the shoe and uniform depart ments The main portion of the store will be devoted primarily to selfservice Checkout cashiers will be increased to a total of five and will be located both in the front and back of the store Salesclerk assistance will be provided in the Appliance De partment to package large items for patrons and to prepare sales slips for those items priced at 500 or more This procedure will eliminate delays which would otherwise be created at the"
